{"tid":716144,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"求救!!ITUNES備份密碼唔記得左","createTime":"2018-06-25T04:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T05:19:17.000Z","uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ea22f7c2f4e99229a47d597b7579d23570d61492","tid":716144,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:42:25.000Z","msg":"請各位巴打救救小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近部6S壞左 見IP8減價 諗住賣左部6S換機<br />\n咁賣之前就BACK UP左之後先去賣<br />\n點知買完新機番黎 想回復既時候發現個備份檔原來有密碼<br />\n但自己又低能 記唔起SET左咩PW<br />\n打去APPLE官方問 佢地話個密碼係電腦到 唔係APPLE個DATA BASE到<br />\n但試左成晚都無計 上網試過幾個ITUNE備分密碼既破解器都係無辦法<br />\n<br />\n有無人可以救到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cca85f62eb0c1bd689b14f612b7c0c1f1cd174","tid":716144,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de5b5a265810e2a1772b8dbf97e0fa86ba9ba336","tid":716144,"uid":111054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"apple官方答覆係唔記得密碼就無法回覆，可以死心"},{"pid":"79471f044bf02a443eb0f09e2d44b3e4fc3a59c9","tid":716144,"uid":111054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de5b5a265810e2a1772b8dbf97e0fa86ba9ba336","tid":716144,"uid":111054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:51:59.000Z","msg":"apple官方答覆係唔記得密碼就無法回覆，可以死心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"係回復"},{"pid":"5d98f06fc57fd53302d13ca851c72385563e45f1","tid":716144,"uid":10068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/25/125610_c6e44aa6b37fe3179c20fb35a7b899fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F25%2F125610_c6e44aa6b37